{"builtWith":"0.15.15","comments":[{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":"                                               // hydrogen // gpu // diffusion"},{"LineComment":" ━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━"},{"LineComment":" | Diffusion — GPU Compute Abstractions for Diffusion Model Inference"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Design Philosophy"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Diffusion models generate images through iterative denoising. This module"},{"LineComment":" | provides **pure data** representing diffusion operations, compatible with:"},{"LineComment":" | - Stable Diffusion (SD 1.5, 2.x, XL, 3.x)"},{"LineComment":" | - Flux, Cascade, and other latent diffusion architectures"},{"LineComment":" | - Video diffusion models (SVD, Mochi, etc.)"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## RES4LYF Integration"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Types are designed for compatibility with res4lyf advanced sampling:"},{"LineComment":" | - Scheduler types matching ComfyUI + res4lyf custom schedulers"},{"LineComment":" | - Noise types: gaussian, brownian, fractal, pyramid variants"},{"LineComment":" | - Noise modes: hard, soft, lorentzian for sigma scaling"},{"LineComment":" | - Guide modes: flow, sync, lure for conditioning guidance"},{"LineComment":" | - Implicit methods: rebound, retro-eta, bongmath, predictor-corrector"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Tensor-Native Model"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Diffusion kernels operate on latent tensors:"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ```"},{"LineComment":" | DiffusionKernel :: LatentTensor -> Conditioning -> NoiseSchedule -> LatentTensor"},{"LineComment":" | ```"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Standard shapes:"},{"LineComment":" | - SD 1.5/2.x: [B, 4, H/8, W/8]"},{"LineComment":" | - SDXL: [B, 4, H/8, W/8]"},{"LineComment":" | - SD3/Flux: [B, 16, H/8, W/8]"},{"LineComment":" | - Cascade: [B, 16, H/42, W/42] stage C, [B, 4, H/4, W/4] stage B"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## At Billion-Agent Scale"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | Diffusion parameters are deterministic data:"},{"LineComment":" | - Same scheduler + noise seed = same generation (always)"},{"LineComment":" | - Kernels can be serialized, hashed, cached across agents"},{"LineComment":" | - Multiple agents can share inference pipelines"},{"LineComment":" | - GPU batches across agents efficiently"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | ## Module Structure"},{"LineComment":" |"},{"LineComment":" | This is a leader module that re-exports from:"},{"LineComment":" | - Hydrogen.GPU.Diffusion.Types — Core types and ADTs"},{"LineComment":" | - Hydrogen.GPU.Diffusion.Kernels — Kernel newtypes and DiffusionConfig"},{"LineComment":" | - Hydrogen.GPU.Diffusion.Region — Region diffusion state"},{"LineComment":" | - Hydrogen.GPU.Diffusion.Config — Default config and presets"},{"LineComment":" | - Hydrogen.GPU.Diffusion.Constructor — Smart constructors"}],"decls":[],"exports":[],"foreign":[],"imports":[{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[219,14],"start":[212,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Diffusion","Config"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[228,19],"start":[221,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Diffusion","Constructor"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[205,15],"start":[187,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Diffusion","Kernels"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[210,14],"start":[207,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Diffusion","Region"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[185,13],"start":[67,1]}},"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Diffusion","Types"]},{"annotation":{"meta":null,"sourceSpan":{"end":[228,19],"start":[55,1]}},"moduleName":["Prim"]}],"moduleName":["Hydrogen","GPU","Diffusion"],"modulePath":"../../hydrogen/src/Hydrogen/GPU/Diffusion.purs","re